text: Abul Kalam Mazumdar () is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Comilla-9. ==Career== Mazumdar was elected to parliament from Comilla-9 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986. ==Death== Mazumdar died on 31 October 1994. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:1994 deaths Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members
title: Abul Kalam Mazumdar
